org.pragmaticminds.crunch.chronicle

Class ChronicleSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pragmaticminds.crunch.chronicle.ChronicleSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, MRecordSource

    public class ChronicleSource
extends Object
implements MRecordSource
    Wrapper around the ChronicleConsumer exposing a MRecordSource interface for usage in Pipelines.

    The connection to the Chronicle Queue on the FS is done in the init() method. Thus this is serializable and can be instantiated multiple times.

    Author:
    julian Created by julian on 21.08.18
